high_descs: Walk to the small bucket next to the toilet to your left .
Grab the roll of toilet paper in the bucket.
Turn to face the toilet to your left.
Place the roll of toilet paper on top of the toilet.
Turn left and then walk to your right to the side of the toilet where the plunger is.
Grab the empty roll on the floor next the toilet.
Turn around, walk straight, make a quick left, walk straight, make a  left when you reach the tub, walk straight to the bucket and turn left when you reach the bucket.
Place the empty roll next to the full roll on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place an empty roll and full roll on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper in the trash can on the floor.
Turn left to face the back of the toilet.
Place the toilet paper on the back of the toilet.
Walk around to face the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the empty roll on the floor.
Look to the right to face the back of the sink.
Place the empty roll on the back of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a roll of toilet paper and an empty roll on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Walk up to the tub, then turn left and walk over to the small bin to the right of the toilet.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper out of the small bin.
Turn right and walk over to the tub, then turn around to face the toilet.
Put the roll of toilet paper on top of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the wall, turn right again and walk up to the wall then look down at the floor.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the ground in front of you.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the tub, turn left again and walk forward then turn left to face the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls to the toilet tank.
